query:
SELECT o.*, om.role 
FROM organizations o
INNER JOIN organization_members om ON o.id = om.organization_id
INNER JOIN users u ON om.user_id = u.id
WHERE u.email = 'wyatt@gtmplanetary.com'
LIMIT 1
